+/*
+ * S3C2410 PLL configuration
+ * -------------------------
+ *
+ * Basic frequency calculation
+ *
+ *            m * REFclk         s = SDIV
+ * PLLclk = ------------         p = PDIV + 2
+ *             p * 2^s           m = MDIV + 8
+ *
+ * After reset the PLL of the s3c2410 processor uses:
+ *
+ *         MPLL   UPLL
+ *  MDIV   0x5c   0x28
+ *  PDIV   0x08   0x08
+ *  SDIV   0x0    0x0
+ *
+ *            100 * 12MHz     1200MHz
+ * MPLLclk = ------------- = -------- = 120MHz
+ *             10 * 2^0         10
+ *
+ *            48 * 12MHz      576MHz
+ * UPLLclk = ------------- = -------- = 57,6MHz
+ *             10 * 2^0        10
+ *
+ * Note: Do not use "r10" here in this code
+ */
+
